channel.title: Trickshotting - MW2 (XBL)
channel.description: Hey guys, I am starting up an xbl lobby atm need 6 ppl to go online S&D trickshot last kill recording with HD PVR. I am hosting clan tryouts after. You may try out.. it is a trickshotting clan so only reply to this if you are a trickshotter and you are good! Any shit killcams you will be kicked and I will hate you forever! Vice versa if you get a good killcam! Comment back your GT and tell me if you are good on a scale of 1 to 10.
